        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You form up with allies and move in unison. Stride once. You can choose up to two willing allies adjacent to you at the start of your movement to move with you as a reaction. All allies end their movement adjacent to you, but not adjacent to one another, forming a line or triangle. Creatures moving with March! can't move further than the lowest Speed used by any other creature in that march.</p>"
